        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Nara Organics recalls baby formula sold at Target after multistate infant botulism outbreak</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Nara Organics has recalled its organic baby formula sold at Target stores and online due to a multistate outbreak of infant botulism.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/06/14/nara-organics-recalls-baby-formula-sold-at-target-after-multistate-infant-botulism-outbreak/"  >(Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
