        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">12 dead in crash of plane on skydiving outing in Missouri, authorities say</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Authorities say a pilot and 11 others were killed when a plane taking people on a skydiving outing in Missouri crashed in a field and caught fire.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/06/14/12-dead-in-crash-of-plane-on-skydiving-outing-in-missouri-authorities-say/"  >(Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
