        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Britain detains sanctioned oil tanker believed to be linked to Russia&#8217;s shadow fleet</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Britain’s armed forces have boarded and detained a sanctioned tanker, the Smyrtos, in the English Channel.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/06/14/britain-detains-sanctioned-oil-tanker-believed-to-be-linked-to-russias-shadow-fleet/"  >(Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
