    <h3 itemprop="headline">Lebanese army withdraws from southern village after Israeli troops advance nearby</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Lebanese army has withdrawn its troops from a base in a southern village after Israeli forces advanced nearby.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/06/13/lebanese-army-withdraws-from-southern-village-after-israeli-troops-advance-nearby/"  >(Bassem Mroue, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
