    <h3 itemprop="headline">Israel fears Trump weary of &#8216;highly suspicious&#8217; Netanyahu and could 'flip' amid Iran deal: analyst</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      An analyst says fears are growing in Jerusalem that President Trump could flip on Netanyahu amid U.S.-Iran deal tensions, with strikes in Beirut complicating talks.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/06/14/israel-fears-trump-weary-highly-suspicious-netanyahu-could-flip-amid-iran-deal-analyst/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
