    <h3 itemprop="headline">Putin, Zelenskyy speak with Trump by phone as drone strikes kill 2 in Russia and UK detains tanker</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy and Russian President Vladimir Putin each spoke by phone with U.S. President Donald Trump on Sunday, marking Trump's 80th birthday and ahead of this week’s G7 summit.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/06/14/ukrainian-drone-strikes-kill-1-and-spark-fire-at-oil-facility-in-russia/"  >(Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
