    <h3 itemprop="headline">Denny Hamlin wins the NASCAR Cup race at Pocono for his third straight victory</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Denny Hamlin is still planning to retire at the end of next season but won the NASCAR Cup Series race at Pocono Raceway for his third consecutive victory.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2026/06/14/denny-hamlin-wins-the-nascar-cup-race-at-pocono-for-his-third-straight-victory/"  >(Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
