        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Havertz sparks Germany&#8217;s 7-1 rout of Cura&#231;ao after underdogs&#8217; historic 1st goal in World Cup</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Kai Havertz scored two goals as Germany pulled away from World Cup first-timer Curaçao late in the opening half and piled on after that in a 7-1 win in a group match.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2026/06/14/havertz-sparks-germanys-7-1-rout-of-curacao-after-underdogs-historic-1st-goal-in-world-cup/"  >(Kristie Rieken, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
