    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump celebrates his 80th birthday with an Iran deal and a UFC cage fight at the White House</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      President Donald Trump is celebrating turning 80 by announcing a preliminary agreement to end the war and a UFC cage-fighting event on the White House lawn.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2026/06/14/trump-turns-80-with-a-showstopping-spectacle-of-cage-fights-at-the-white-house-but-big-issues-loom/"  >(Will Weissert, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
