    <h3 itemprop="headline">Lawsuit alleges soccer coach benched teen who was injured by teammate for alleged racial slur</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A New York family alleges a Christian school and the Archdiocese of New York failed to supervise students before a soccer event, injuring a teen.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2026/06/14/lawsuit-alleges-soccer-coach-benched-teen-injured-teammate-alleged-racial-slur/"  >(Fox News)</a>
