        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Knicks beat Spurs in Game 5 to win first NBA championship since 1973, ending 53-year drought</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Knicks capped one of the most memorable seasons in franchise history Saturday night, beating the Spurs 94-90 in Game 5 of the NBA Finals to win their first championship since 1973.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2026/06/14/knicks-beat-spurs-game-5-win-first-nba-championship-since-1973-ending-53-year-drought/"  >(Fox News)</a>
