    <h3 itemprop="headline">Georgia's vote-counting method will soon be banned. Lawmakers will try to find a fix this week</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Georgia lawmakers are expected to try to clean up an election mess of their own making when they return to the Capitol this week for a special session.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/06/14/georgias-vote-counting-method-will-soon-be-banned-lawmakers-will-try-to-find-a-fix-this-week/"  >(Kate Brumback, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
