    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump names James M. McDonald to lead powerful New York federal prosecutor's office</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      President Donald Trump says he will appoint one of his personal lawyers to serve as the top federal prosecutor in Manhattan, filling a pending vacancy after Trump tapped the man currently in the job to be director of national intelligence.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/06/13/trump-names-james-m-mcdonald-to-lead-powerful-new-york-federal-prosecutors-office/"  >(Fatima Hussein And Eric Tucker, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
