    <h3 itemprop="headline">How property tax relief will reach Minnesota homeowners</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Lawmakers added to an existing tax relief program after many homeowners saw steep increases to their annual property taxes.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/06/10/how-minnesotas-homestead-credit-increase-offsets-higher-property-taxes/"  >(Peter Cox, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
