        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump picks James McDonald to lead powerful Southern District of New York after Jay Clayton's departure</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      President Donald Trump announces intent to appoint James M. McDonald as the next U.S. attorney for SDNY, replacing Jay Clayton who was nominated as DNI director.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/06/13/trump-picks-james-mcdonald-lead-powerful-southern-district-new-york-jay-claytons-departure/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 13 Jun 2026 12:34:50 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 13 Jun 2026 12:34:50 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fatima Hussein, Associated Press, Local 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/06/13/inside-the-crowd-drawn-to-trumps-unusual-ufc-fight-night-at-the-white-house.webp" alt="Inside the crowd drawn to Trump's unusual UFC fight night at the White House" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Inside the crowd drawn to Trump's unusual UFC fight night at the White House</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Throngs of UFC fans have descended on the nation's capital for an unusual fight night at the White House.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/06/13/inside-the-crowd-drawn-to-trumps-unusual-ufc-fight-night-at-the-white-house/"  >(Fatima Hussein, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 14 Jun 2026 18:31:23 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 14 Jun 2026 18:31:23 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/06/14/congressional-baseball-game-offers-longstanding-traditions-plenty-confusion.webp" alt="Congressional baseball game offers longstanding traditions, and plenty of confusion" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Congressional baseball game offers longstanding traditions, and plenty of confusion</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The annual Congressional baseball game poses unique challenges as lawmakers on the same team wear duplicate uniform numbers, making broadcasts tricky.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/06/14/congressional-baseball-game-offers-longstanding-traditions-plenty-confusion/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
